## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="53d5a-132">這個屬性會以百分比表示的 y 軸刻度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="53d5a-132">This property is measured as a percentage of the Y-axis scale.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="53d5a-133">根據預設，其值設為 25。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="53d5a-133">By default, its value is set to 25.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="53d5a-134">這表示數列中的資料點有至少 25%的小數位數的差異，將會摺疊具有刻度斷層。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="53d5a-134">This means that data points in a series that have a difference of at least 25% of the scale will be collapsed with a scale break.</span></span>  
  
   
  
